snippet.title: Job Joust - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2800510/Job_Joust/
The Demo of Job Joust is finally available on Steam!

Features of the Demo:
- 4 Player local or online (with Steam Remote Play Together)  👨‍👩‍👦‍👦
- 16 stages 🌍
- 45 items 🌂
- 6 different characters 👮‍♂️
- Near infinite build combinations 🫨
- Bots (not everybody has friends :') )
